Consumption: ru=0 kvru=0  reads=0 in 0 batches (0 bytes)  writes=0 in 0 batches (0 bytes)  pod-cpu-usage: 0 secs  pgwire-egress=0 bytes  external-egress=0 bytes  external-ingress=0 bytes
